items.title: Peachy Sands
items.description: Discover the beauty and serenity of the shore with our latest NFT project! Featuring clean and simplistic 3D beach illustrations in a tranquil shade of pink, this collection captures the essence of beach life with playful flamingos adding a touch of fun. Immerse yourself in this tranquil digital world and bring a piece of the beach to your NFT portfolio.

items.title: Absrart Collection
items.description: Step into a world of bold and vibrant art with our latest NFT project! This collection features abstract designs in contrasting colors, creating visually striking pieces that are sure to make a statement.

items.title: Aquatech
items.description: Introducing the most unique and captivating NFT project yet! The project features an extraordinary collection of robot fish, each one expertly crafted with intricate details and stunning animations, creating an underwater world unlike anything you've ever seen before. Get ready to dive in and explore the depths of this mesmerizing digital realm!

items.title: The Bubblemotes
items.description: Get ready to pop with excitement! Our newest NFT project features a world of bubbles, each one uniquely designed with an expressive face that captures a wide range of emotions. From joyful grins to cheeky winks, these bubbles will bring a playful energy to your NFT collection.

items.title: Venom Network
items.description: This digital collectibles marks your involvement in testing Venom products.

items.title: Venom Testnet & OneArt
items.description: Owners of these digital collectibles are individuals who participated in the Venom Testnet using the OneArt Wallet.

items.title: Numi Stories, Club 404 Grand Opening
items.description: Get early access to multiplayer functionality in Numiverse Numi Stories mobile game.
